<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior bide a wile motel evening}
<A>__{mitchell stephens is having a meeting with wendell and risa walker in their livingroom behind the reception area. mitchell has a pad of paper and is taking notes.}
<C>__{wendell}
<D>__{kyle lambston's a drunk. nobody likes him. he's a nasty piece of work.}
